---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const title = 'Video Extension';
---

<DocsLayout title={title}>
<h1>Video Extension</h1>
<p>Extend an existing video using <code>POST /v1/videos/extensions</code>. The <code>duration</code> parameter specifies the extension length only (not total video length).</p>
<pre><code>{`curl -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/videos/extensions \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "video": "https://example.com/source.mp4",
    "prompt": "Continue the scene smoothly",
    "duration": 5
  }'`}</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
